name: ONTARIO STREET THEATRE in Port Hope.
blurb: We're an affordable theatre and rental space that can be molded into anything by anyone.

name: December Match Campaign
blurb: By matching donations up to $5000, Jack Kesler and Maurice Richards have challenged YOU to help Urbanite outfit their brand new space.

blurb: STC & the Sheboygan Area School District are working tirelessly to renovate our 30-year-old sound system. Help us sound better for you!

blurb: Help Synetic Theater create a new Studio to produce amazing  shows in the 2013/14 season and train awesome artists of all ages!

name: Shelter the Schmee

blurb: We plan to transition from 35mm to the new digital projection format to continue to show current first run films for our community.

blurb: Be part of building Cardiff's first pub theatre, located right in the city centre. Launching January 2015.

blurb: Let there be sound! Make our new theatre more accessible by installing a modern sound and hearing assistance system for our audience.

name: The Red Shoes
blurb: We're aiming to launch a production involving circus performers, musicians and artists in a new space, creating a night of live art.

name: A Sign for 34 West
blurb: We're turning an old yogurt shop into a live theater in downtown Charleston.   Please help us hang our sign!

name: House of Yes

blurb: Help us build a 200 seat theater and classroom space in North Andover, MA. Let's get kids off the screens, and into the spotlight!

name: Colorado ACTS Black Box Painting
blurb: Walmart decided they wanted our space, so we had to move to a new theater. Help us make it an awesome space by painting it all black!

name: improvMANIA Improv Comedy Theater - Chandler, Arizona

name: Hippity Hip: An eco-friendly playspace and parent lounge
blurb: Hippity Hip is an eco-friendly playspace in Rochester, NY where children and parents can come together to play and socialize.

name: The New Sky Candy
blurb: In 2018, Sky Candy will move to a new studio. Help us transform it into the best aerial & circus arts space in Austin, TX!

name: Save the Malibu Playhouse
blurb: Lets save this iconic playhouse from extinction and preserve it for future generations. This should not be removed from our community,

name: Downtown Cowtown at the Isis, FW Stockyards
blurb:
Reviving a historic Theatre, becoming a premiere
provider of quality live theatrical performances, movies, entertainment, and more.

name: ENVISION OUR THEATER for Special Needs, Vets & At-Risk Youth
blurb: Be part of the community that will build a theater for underserved youth, individuals with special needs, and military veterans.

name: Save The Ridgewood!
blurb: The Ridgewood Theater is different things to everyone who has memories of it. It is a cornerstone of Queens, NY. and deserves a RETURN!

blurb: SHE&HER PRODUCTIONS! New Space.. New SHOW! We have a home in KC West Bottoms, the Crane Building. We need your help turning this space into a theater!

name: Help Fund the "Back Room" Arts Space at Jimmy's No 43!

name: The Coalition Theater
blurb: Help create a permanent home for live comedy shows and classes in Downtown RVA.
